Invocation Name: free fun
des: This skill will enable you to hear the latest blog post from Free Fun in Austin. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done. Any time you're ready for more -- and there's new content on Free Fun in Austin every single day -- just say "Alexa, start free fun" and our words will fill your ears. That's all there is to it!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
